title: Arbor Skateboards :: Adam Crigler Los Angeles Spot Check
description: Usually when we drop a new Adam Crigler video, he's ripping up New York so we decided to get him out of his element and bring him to sunny SoCal and the big city on the West Coast that is Los Angles. This Spot Check features Crigler slashing around the LA area with his favorite urban destroyer… the Arbor Catalyst. This one will make you want to go skate the streets of a big city near you.
